{"title":"老的和小的","authors":["亦门"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":12,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"老的和小的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老祖父走在到托儿所去的路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好太阳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼吸着，空气就是奶花香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墙上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常春藤的叶子鲜红了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像来接红儿的老祖父一样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当下工回家，在泥泞的街道上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸给美国吉普车辗死了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红儿是遗腹子；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天还在下雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人还在哭泣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈又死于产褥热——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红儿成了孤儿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红儿哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红儿是祖父的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小宝贝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖父不笑，红儿笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红儿笑了，祖父皱着眉头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陪着红儿笑开了嘴："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个没有长牙齿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个牙齿没有了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪花和红旗——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"托儿所迎接红儿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖父在红星下修理机器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——好手艺！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖父"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱机器一样爱红儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱红儿一样爱机器。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖父接红儿，在风雪的日子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖父自己解开热腾腾的棉衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把红儿仔细地裹紧在怀里："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖父的体温"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫着孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子的体温"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感动了老人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏天，人们沿路吃冰棒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖父躬着背，推小藤车；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从藤车的小花孔里流过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从孩子的花衣襟上流过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从孩子的笑脸上流过。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也从老人的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慈祥的心里流过。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在“控美大会上”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖父流着眼泪说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“修理机器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修理枪！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从“控美大会”出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖父去接红儿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在街道这面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行进着“抗美援朝”的志愿军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在街道那面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打着“保家卫国”的红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖父感到，他是走在队伍里面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的脚步合着进行曲的节奏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的心，和腰鼓一同响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨恨地想着吉普车，想着红儿的爹和娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖父看到红儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看到一个红儿和无数红儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红儿们向祖父笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖父向红儿们笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖父心里发誓："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决不能让中国的孩子再像红儿一样！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子的生活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是和平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子要苹果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要战争。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能让"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战争冲进祖国的大门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用战争去反对战争！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五○年十一月十九日。天津。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}